      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Shadow in the Jungle",
        "Client": "Covert Trainee",
        "Description": "I am taught to be one with the shadows\r\nbut never have I seen a shadow move\r\nthrough the Jungle at such tremendous\r\nspeed. What could it have been? An\r\nassassin from a rival clan? A spirit?\r\nNevertheless, such a threat cannot\r\nbe allowed to exist. Eliminate it.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Ombres dans la jungle",
        "Client": "Apprenti camoufl\u00E9",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai vu un truc bizarre sur la route\r\nun soir... Une ombre noire volant\r\nvers la Jungle \u00E0 toute vitesse\r\net laissant des entailles profondes\r\ndans les arbres. On ne peut pas\r\nlaisser cette chose s\u0027approcher\r\nde l\u0027Avant-poste.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Gli assassini del sottobosco",
        "Client": "Apprendista sotto copertura",
        "Description": "Ho visto qualcosa di strano per\r\nstrada a notte fonda: un\u0027ombra\r\nnera che volava verso la giungla\r\na velocit\u00E0 incredibile, seguita\r\nda profondi tagli sugli alberi\r\nlungo la strada. Non lasciare\r\nche si avvicini all\u0027avamposto!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schatten in Dschungel",
        "Client": "Heimlicher Sch\u00FCler",
        "Description": "Mir wurde beigebracht, eins mit\r\nden Schatten zu sein, aber nie\r\nhabe ich einen Schatten gesehen,\r\nder sich so durch den Dschungel\r\nbewegte. Was k\u00F6nnte es gewesen\r\nsein? Ein Geist? Diese Bedrohung\r\ndarf nicht bestehen bleiben!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Nargacuga.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Sombras en la Jungla",
        "Client": "Aprendiz encubierto",
        "Description": "Me han ense\u00F1ado a moverme como\r\nlas sombras, pero nunca hab\u00EDa\r\nvisto una moverse tan r\u00E1pido por\r\nla Jungla. \u00BFQu\u00E9 habr\u00E1 sido eso?\r\n\u00BFUn asesino de otro clan? \u00BFUn\r\nesp\u00EDritu? En todo caso, no puedo\r\ntolerar amenazas as\u00ED. Elim\u00EDnala.",
        "Target": "Caza un Nargacuga",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041B\u0435\u0441\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u0443\u0431\u0438\u0439\u0446\u044B",
